# GitHub Personal Access Token used only by local integration/e2e tests
# (pnpm test:integration / pnpm test:e2e) — never by the app itself.
#
# Scope it minimally: a fine-grained token with read-only public-repository
# access is enough. The tests only resolve the token's own identity and read
# github.com/octocat/Hello-World, a public repo — never grant write access
# or access to private resources for a token meant only for test runs.
#
# Copy this file to .env (already gitignored) and fill in a real value.
GITHUB_TEST_PAT=
